name: Skyline_Furniture_Inset_Nail_Button_Headboard_in_Micro-Suede_Charcoal
reviews: Looks great in my daughters room and will transition well from the pre-teen to the teen years. She loves it. Easy to assemble and not bad quality for the price. I like that the back is fully covered as well.
description: Incorporate a high-end touch into your bedroom with the pewter nailhead outline on this Skyline Furniture headboard. With rich charcoal microsuede upholstery, this headboard complements darker furniture and provides a pleasant contrast to lighter tones.
